name: Mistile
tag_list: private-online-sales, clothing, fashion, designer, apparel, luxury, shopping, deals, lifestyle, ecommerce, flash-sales, members-only, community, middle-east, discount
overview: Mistile is an online private shopping community where high end brands are discounted at up to 70% off retail. Dedicated to provide its members a unique shopping experience with access to a curated selection of some of the world best coveted fashion and luxury lifestyle brands limited over a period of time. Mistile selection includes product offerings across the apparel, accessories, home, shoes, kids and lifestyle categories. Membership is free and by invitation only.
